    {
      "slug": "inner-space-cave-austin",
      "title": "Inner Space Cave Tour — Austin, Texas",
      "date": "2025-03-22",
      "tags": ["cave", "texas", "family-trip", "geology"],
      "excerpt": "A underground adventure through limestone formations right in the Texas Hill Country.",
      "primaryImage": "v1777680831/F20AB199-8935-4DE4-9F18-76BEBF78A9D1_1_105_c_d7xz7x",
      "stats": {
        "distance": "1.2 mi",
        "elevation": "n/a",
        "difficulty": "easy"
      },
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": "Inner Space Cavern is a karst cave discovered in 1963 during construction of Interstate 35. We took the Adventure Tour which goes through some of the most spectacular formations."
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "v1777680831/F20AB199-8935-4DE4-9F18-76BEBF78A9D1_1_105_c_d7xz7x",
          "alt": "Entrance to Inner Space Cavern"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": "The stalactites and stalagmites were incredible. Our guide explained that some of these formations are over 100,000 years old."
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "v1777680826/79966570-29B6-4473-BCDE-740EBB8C2867_1_105_c_v9zvae",
          "alt": "Stalactite formations inside the cave"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": "The temperature stays around 72 degrees year-round, which was a welcome break from the Texas heat above ground."
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "v1777680819/F89D30AA-BDDB-4E71-A098-29436AE8278A_1_105_c_f3vuwq",
          "alt": "Flowstone formations in the cave"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": "The kids loved the section where the guide turned off all the lights to show true cave darkness — you literally couldn't see your hand an inch from your face."
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "v1777680813/33B94973-C3BF-4023-8DD2-DE9060E2B0D1_1_105_c_d9oin2",
          "alt": "Family photo inside Inner Space Cavern"
        }
      ]
    },
